page.title: 12INDUSTRY
page.content: There are no large industries in our D block.However there are a few small companies in the Botley area.These are the Botley Flour Milling Company and Roxburgh and Scivier Industrial{ Fuels. {LANDSCAPE-WOODLAND} There are no shops in our D block,but there are a few nurseries and houses.The land-cover is mainly woodland,consisting of oak,beech,silver birch and yew trees.The ground cover is brambles,bracken and dead leaves,ivy and twigs.The woodland consists of many wild animals like badgers,rabbits,squirrels,foxes,deer, fieldmice,stoats,water-rats and moles. {LANGUAGE} Many people can speak French to get by.
